---
title: Arugula and Pesto Pizza with Feta Cheese
description: Zucchini, pesto and feta cheese top this savoury and indulgent pizza with light, flaky phyllo pastry instead of traditional pizza dough! Toasted almonds add an unmistakable crunch to the arugula salad which is dressed in a sweet and sticky fig jam!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pizza-au-pesto-et-a-la-roquette-9040294d.jpg
